<%- include('../partials/user-head', { title: 'About Us' }) %>

<body class="bg-black text-light">

<%- include('../partials/header') %>

<!-- HERO -->
<!-- HERO -->
<header class="hero-section d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center text-center"
style="height:60vh;min-height:400px;background-image:url('https://res.cloudinary.com/deutxfkar/image/upload/v1773056647/6.-pe600814_color-1024x713_nuntjk.jpg');background-size:cover;background-position:center;margin-top:76px;border-bottom:4px solid #E63946;">
<div class="container position-relative z-2">
<h1 class="display-3 fw-bold text-uppercase hero-title">Our <span class="text-danger">Story</span></h1>
<p class="lead text-white-50">Exploring the Universe of Imagination</p>
</div>
<div class="hero-overlay"></div>
</header>


<section class="py-5 border-bottom border-secondary">
<div class="container">
<div class="row justify-content-center">
<div class="col-lg-10">

<h2 class="fw-bold text-danger mb-4">What are comics?</h2>

<p class="lead text-secondary">
Comics are a medium used to express ideas through images, often combined with text or visual storytelling.
</p>

<p class="text-white-50">
It typically takes the form of sequential panels that guide the reader through a narrative. Dialogue,
narration and sound effects are expressed through speech balloons, captions and visual symbols.
</p>

<p class="text-white-50">
Across history, comics evolved differently across cultures. American superhero comics, European
graphic novels and Japanese manga shaped modern storytelling.
</p>

<p class="text-white-50">
Today comics represent art, philosophy, creativity and imagination.
</p>

</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>


<!-- ABOUT COMIZON -->
<section class="py-5 bg-dark border-bottom border-secondary">
<div class="container">
<div class="row align-items-center">

<div class="col-lg-6 mb-4">

<h2 class="fw-bold mb-3">
Welcome to <span class="text-danger">COMIZON</span>
</h2>

<p class="lead text-white">
At COMIZON, we believe stories shape the way we see the world.
</p>

<p class="text-white-50">
What started as a love for comic books has grown into a premium destination
for collectors, readers and enthusiasts.
</p>

<p class="text-white-50">
From iconic American comics and legendary manga to collectibles and figurines,
Comizon brings imagination and storytelling together.
</p>

<h4 class="text-danger mt-4">Our Mission</h4>

<p class="text-white-50">
Celebrate imagination, reward curiosity and empower readers to explore worlds beyond reality.
</p>

</div>

<div class="col-lg-6 text-center">

<div class="p-5 border border-secondary">
<i class="fas fa-book-open fa-5x text-danger mb-3"></i>

<h3 class="logo-text">
READ BOLD.<br>
COLLECT SMART.<br>
THINK DEEPER.
</h3>

</div>

</div>

</div>
</div>
</section>



<!-- WHAT WE OFFER -->
<section class="py-5 border-bottom border-secondary">

<div class="container">

<h2 class="text-center fw-bold mb-5">What We Offer</h2>

<div class="row g-4">

<div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3">
<div class="p-4 border border-secondary h-100">
<i class="fas fa-mask fa-2x text-danger mb-3"></i>
<h4 class="fw-bold">American Comics</h4>
<p class="text-white-50 small">Classic and modern titles from legendary universes.</p>
</div>
</div>

<div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3">
<div class="p-4 border border-secondary h-100">
<i class="fas fa-book fa-2x text-danger mb-3"></i>
<h4 class="fw-bold">Manga</h4>
<p class="text-white-50 small">From timeless favorites to trending Japanese series.</p>
</div>
</div>

<div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3">
<div class="p-4 border border-secondary h-100">
<i class="fas fa-robot fa-2x text-danger mb-3"></i>
<h4 class="fw-bold">Collectibles</h4>
<p class="text-white-50 small">Premium action figures and collector merchandise.</p>
</div>
</div>

<div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3">
<div class="p-4 border border-warning h-100">
<i class="fas fa-microscope fa-2x text-warning mb-3"></i>
<h4 class="fw-bold text-warning">Be Skeptic</h4>
<p class="text-white-50 small">Scientific and rational books for curious minds.</p>
</div>
</div>

</div>
</div>

</section>



