We believe curiosity deserves rewards.
</h2>

<ul class="list-unstyled text-white-50">

<li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-check text-warning me-2"></i> Exclusive skeptic section</li>
<li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-check text-warning me-2"></i> Premium products</li>
<li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-check text-warning me-2"></i> Early access to releases</li>
<li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-check text-warning me-2"></i> Knowledge focused community</li>

</ul>

<p class="fw-bold">
Available for $100 / $6000 — one-time membership.
</p>

